title: Grateful Dead Live at Madison Square Garden on 1987-09-19
lineage: Nak DR-2>Tascam CDRW2000>CD; Extraction: CD>xACT 1.69 (cdparanoia)>WAV>FLAC, all tracks extracted with no errors
description:
Set 1

Mississippi Half Step, It's All Over Now, High Time, Mexicali Blues-> Big River, When Push Comes To Shove, Box Of Rain-> Don't Ease Me In

Set 2

Crazy Fingers-> Uncle John's Band-> Playin' In The Band-> Drums-> Jam-> I Need A Miracle-> Maggie's Farm-> Black Peter-> Around & Around-> Turn On Your Love Light, E: Black Muddy River

TV Broadcast for Farm Aid

reviews.review_text: Turn it up! This show will not disappoint the careful listener.  Lots of bandwidth retained.  Bright, good levels…hear the Garden in its resonant glory, filled with the same energy as the night before. How about that setlist?!   “All I want to know is, ‘Are you kind?!’”
